The paper discusses the design and implementation of a middleware system for pervasive homecare environment, which involves the use of artificial intelligence and cyber systems to assist inhabitants in their daily tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
